instructions: Put the Charger on Table Cloth
Put the Dinner Fork immediately to the left of the Charger
Put the Dinner Knife immediately to the right of the Charger.
Put the Salad Fork immediately to the left of the Dinner Fork
Put Salad Knife immediately to the right of the Dinner Knife
Put Salad Spoon immediately to the right of the Salad Knife
Put Dessert Spoon above the Charger pointing its head towards left  side
Put the Dessert Fork in between Charger and Dessert Spoon pointing its head towards right side
Put the Bread Plate above the Salad Fork
Put Butter Knife on the Bread Plate
Put Water Glass above the Salad Knife
